Description: A pkgdown template package that provides consistent styling and
    layout for R package documentation sites maintained by the Economic Policy
    Institute. Use this package as the template in your pkgdown configuration
    to apply EPI branding and defaults.
URL: https://economic.github.io/epitemplate/, https://github.com/Economic/epitemplate
